Aku juga mau teken.

594
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:32,880
Jangan berdesakan.

595
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:34,310
Sebentar lagi giliran kalian.

596
00:29:34,430 --> 00:29:35,680
Satu per satu.

597
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,500
Benar-benar dikasih.

598
